    * [How to install python packages in your Jupyter Notebook server](#motd-how-to-install-python-packages-in-your-jupyter-notebook-server)
  * [Rstudio Server](#motd-rstudio-server)
    * [Get started with Rstudio on FAS OnDemand](#motd-get-started-with-rstudio-on-fas-ondemand)
    * [Troubleshooting Rstudio on FAS OnDemand](#motd-troubleshooting-rstudio-on-fas-ondemand)
      * [Restarting Rstudio](#motd-restarting-rstudio)
